1. Plaque scores were analyzed.
2. A reduction in plaque index was observed after using herbal-based toothpastes.
3. Two different types of herbal-based toothpastes were used.
4. One type of toothpaste was TTO-based.
5. Another type of toothpaste was Meswak-based.
6. Meswak-based toothpaste resulted in significantly less plaque than TTO-based toothpaste.
